<div class="welcome_box">
  SocialMapper let's you create a map with your own places on it to share with whomever you wish.
  <br />
  If you've seen a map you want to modify, you can do that as well! Just find the map and click "Clone" to make your own copy.
</div>
<h1>Listing maps</h1>

<table>
  <tr>
    <th>Name</th>
    <th>Description</th>
    <th></th>
    <th></th>
    <th></th>
  </tr>

<% @maps.each do |map| %>
  <tr>
    <td><%= map.name %></td>
    <td><%= map.description %></td>
    <td><%= link_to 'Show', map %></td>
    <td><%= link_to 'Edit', edit_map_path(map) %></td>
    <td><%= link_to 'Destroy', map, :confirm => 'Are you sure?', :method => :delete %></td>
  </tr>
<% end %>
</table>

<br />

<%= link_to 'New Map', new_map_path %>
